text: Baranovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Chernoyarsky Selsoviet, Chernoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 28 as of 2010. == Geography == It is located 6 km from Chyorny Yar. == References == Category:Rural localities in Chernoyarsky District
title: Baranovka, Chernoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
